353,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873f33bf6f967301587a8e35c4ff708958daf21d","tid":51353,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"畜牲減玄牛"},{"pid":"e77b48a03866a22c8f0fca9a9f8fd7cc6684188d","tid":51353,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e380685afad1feca0e3271e2c6e603c22f8784d9","tid":51353,"uid":43993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等同大陸強拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾年燒過仲跟學校係果邊做field study<br />\n類似係研究個生態既自行修復能力<br />\n大約半年左右d花草樹木蛇蟲鼠蟻就回復原狀<br />\n基本上可以cover返晒燒左既地方<br />\n想強拆應該燒得唔夠多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1127dc932ecfec4f9f3c98cc294ccb4b907f5d7c","tid":51353,"uid":46857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:35:56.000Z","msg":"屌 南生圍做乜撚野要起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d842fe89af950c46398fa408a308cc73e105f09","tid":51353,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒左就係你架啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班仆街覺得，你地想珍惜既野，而家一把火燒哂佢，乜都無，爛地一遍，你地仲有咩值得保留？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c915c1f4d239775b41e1d1044b4bb07cef4c96e","tid":51353,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"